Thus they were political clubs within the tribus, founded often by the candidates themselves, as by P. So the old evil reappeared in a new form. Hence such a collegium is calledffl a consensio quae magis honeste quam vere sodalitas nominatur, because it is not really a sodalitas in the primary sense of the word.
